        {
            "title": "BCA Research轉為中性看待美股,跟隨滙豐銀行步伐",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.130ucTWhmOBTs8AJXOEJw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA9Q076_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <span>BCA Research</span>已將其對美國股市的立場轉為中性,此舉與滙豐銀行週四的類似舉動相呼應,此前修訂後的就業數據顯示,勞動市場的疲軟程度遠超此前的認知。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在一份新報告中,BCA Research表示,年度薪資數據修訂顯示「2025年薪資增長比先前估計的更為吝嗇,且更加集中於狹窄領域」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構強調,薪資增長「在2024年8月就跌破了我們的停滯速度門檻,而非2025年6月」,然而企業盈利和整體經濟卻「毫無阻礙地持續前行」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f38a2ad1-2a9f-3e0c-bbca-24d0b3503eab-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據BCA的分析,包括財富增長和更強大的社會安全網在內的結構性變化,已削弱了「薪酬對消費的影響力」,幫助家庭度過了招聘放緩的時期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管去年大部分時間支出增長超過收入增長,但BCA Research表示「1月份收入激增縮小了這一差距」,並補充稱《一項宏大美好法案》「應有助於進一步縮小差距,因為納稅人將獲得退稅」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在此背景下,BCA Research「對美國即將陷入衰退的擔憂有所減少」,但仍調整了其全球配置策略。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構寫道:「我們已將美國下調至等權重,並將歐元區上調至全球股票投資組合中的等權重。」該機構還將美元下調至低配,同時將歐元上調至等權重。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在固定收益方面,BCA Research已取消其對利率優於信貸的偏好,這反映出該機構認為儘管就業增長放緩,但「經濟擴張仍保持完好」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/bca-research%E8%BD%89%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E6%80%A7%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%85%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1-%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%A8%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%90-135555662.html",
